  "description": "Phase-24d: Phase-23 readout test with the multiset-invariance flaw fixed. Statistic = sum of greedy bipartite-assignment length-scores (each seal used at most once). Null = random one-to-one name<->seal assignments (2000 perms, seed=42). Unlike Phase-23c which always returned p=1.0, this null genuinely varies. Output: reports/phase24d_readout_test_v2.json.",
